    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Leaving Kosi Bay I took with me only the red circles on my feet as a memory - once again nostalgic - of the chafe that bodyboard fins give you. Let’s hope they don’t hurt in the Drakensberg. ",
